OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FRussian President Vladimir Putin has
OL,7,Fhailed the "truly unprecedented level"
OL,8,Fof ties between Moscow and Beijing on
OL,9,Fhis visit to China, days after the
OL,10,Fnation hosted US President Donald
OL,11,FTrump.
OL,13,FThe Russian leader met with Chinese
OL,14,FPresident Xi Jinping at the Great Hall
OL,15,Fof the People on Wednesday morning,
OL,16,Fwhere a large-scale welcome ceremony
OL,17,Fwas held for his arrival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
