OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FCrowds of children holding Russian and
OL,7,FChinese flags were there to greet the
OL,8,Ftwo delegations, as well as the
OL,9,Fmilitary honour guard.
