OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FThe leaders later held bilateral
OL,7,Ftalks, where Putin invited Xi to
OL,8,FRussia next year and told him the
OL,9,Frelationship between their two nations
OL,10,Fhad reached a "truly unprecedented
OL,11,Flevel", according to Chinese media
OL,12,Fowned by China's Communist Party.
OL,14,FThey are expected to attend a ceremony
OL,15,Ffor signing cooperation agreements
OL,16,Flater on Wednesday and will discuss
OL,17,Fenergy and security as well as their
OL,18,Foverall ties.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
