OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FChina became Russia's top trading
OL,7,Fpartner following after Moscow's full-
OL,8,Fscale invasion of Ukraine in 2022,
OL,9,Fwhich caused the US and Europe to
OL,10,Fissue economic and financial sanctions
OL,11,Fon the nation.
OL,13,FBeijing has said its stance on the war
OL,14,Fis neutral and has maintained trade
OL,15,Fties with the Kremlin, as well
OL,16,Fignoring demands from the West to stop
OL,17,Fproviding high-tech components for
OL,18,FRussia's weapons industries.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
