PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779271612
OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FIt is also the top customer for
OL,7,FRussian energy, and Moscow expects the
OL,8,FIran war to increase demand, as China
OL,9,Fis the largest importer of oil from
OL,10,Fthe Gulf nations.
OL,12,FPutin described talks with Xi and
OL,13,Ftheir delegations on Wednesday as
OL,14,F"substantive", Russian news agency
OL,15,FTass reported.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
