OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,F"We have just held substantive talks
OL,7,Fin a traditionally friendly and trust-
OL,8,Fbased atmosphere, addressing bilateral
OL,9,Fcooperation with a limited circle of
OL,10,Fdelegates. Now, we are going to hold
OL,11,Fan extended conversation," Putin said.
OL,13,FPutin's visit comes just days after
OL,14,FTrump's own trip to Beijing in a
OL,15,Fsequence that many experts believe is
OL,16,Fmeant to cement Beijing's image as an
OL,17,Finfluential superpower.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
