CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1779271612
OL,3,CPutin hails 'unprecedented level' of
OL,4,Cties with China on Beijing visit
OL,6,FRussian presidential aide Yuri Ushakov
OL,7,Fsaid earlier that there was "no
OL,8,Fconnection" between Trump and Putin's
OL,9,Fvisits, noting the trip by the Russian
OL,10,Fleader was agreed several days after
OL,11,FPutin and Xi spoke in February.
OL,13,FTrump's meeting with Xi had been
OL,14,Fplanned for April, but was rescheduled
OL,15,Fto May due to the Iran war.
